frontmatter.title: Inset (HC.gov)
frontmatter.intro: The Inset component is meant to draw attention to important content, or to associate a block of content with another element.

status.note: Usage and accessibility guidance is incomplete. Maturity checklist is not documented. Accessibility testing has not been performed.
